## Self-Check Questions

Before committing, ask yourself:
1. Does this stick to "small and beautiful" positioning?
2. Did I introduce unnecessary complexity?
3. Did I implement unrequested features?
4. Did I violate external content compliance principles?

If any answer is "no", fix it before committing.
